TextParameterSet.text: Unlimited Projects...
Flash'iteasy lets you create/duplicate/edit any type of projects : Websites, banners, keynotes. As much projects as you want online and on a single licence fee.
Unlimited Designs...
With no mandatory template, Flash'iteasy entitles yor designers to work in a familiar environment as well as present their sketches interactively at short notice
Use as many pages as you want, whatever complexity is required by your tree structure. Even the size of pages can vary during navigation so you can change universe.
Unlimited Structure...
Unlimited Creation...
Use your own specific fonts, animate your contents, design and mix filters and effects, all without a single line of code.
Unlimited Developpement...
If Flash'iteasy doesn't do it, you can! More than ab API, Flash'iteasy boots your coders with a global framework that entitle them to create complex objects to be added and manage at run time.
You can help-us enhance the Flash'iteasy Framework by sharing your developments and join the community..
Unlimited Extensibility...
FlashIt easy CMS is created for Flash developers, design studios and freelancers who make money on creating and maintaining Flash websites.
Why use it?
What it is?
FlashitEasy CMS is an advanced Flash content management system that allows you to create attractive, functional and SEO- friendly Flash websites.
Who is it for?
With FlashItEasy CMS you can earn more either by creating manageable Flash sites and components for them or by maintaining the created Flash site.
